{"tid":2393972,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國政府：歡迎台灣於蓋亞那設立外交辦公室","createTime":"2021-02-04T01:14:11.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-05T02:47:41.000Z","uid":134071,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"f3ac5818cdd06305cb5c796d926ae14996f763e4","tid":2393972,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T01:14:11.000Z","msg":"（呢句野足以擊中小粉紅玻璃心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n美國政府：歡迎台灣於蓋亞那設立外交辦公室.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/WHAAsstSecty/status/1357112314017837058\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FWHAAsstSecty%2Fstatus%2F1357112314017837058&d=f02Xtm2mX5FaAGCExHUdjctxnk%2BhbBpP3j1S%2FgfPRD4%3D&h=87d312dd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FWHAAsstSecty%2Fstatus%2F1357112314017837058&h=93d99b79\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/WHAAsstSecty/status/1357112314017837058</a>"},{"pid":"99410c419a7fb924850ed0e9c7238c67fb5e2641","tid":2393972,"uid":134071,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T01:15:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/news.aspx?newsid=892921\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fnews.aspx%3Fnewsid%3D892921&d=f02Xtm2mX5FaAGCExHUdjctxnk%2BhbBpP3j1S%2FgfPRD4%3D&h=65318502\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fnews.aspx%3Fnewsid%3D892921&h=7bb172dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/news.aspx?newsid=892921</a>"},{"pid":"a46dc1b226cca11c6bd2c8da05c53675a771570a","tid":2393972,"uid":179729,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T01:16:54.000Z","msg":"Guyana依個地方有特別？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7071bd59a73dd5a3e102771f05352a1ce67e75d","tid":2393972,"uid":197563,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"a46dc1b226cca11c6bd2c8da05c53675a771570a","tid":2393972,"uid":179729,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T01:16:54.000Z","msg":"Guyana依個地方有特別？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T01:17:54.000Z","msg":"Rum and sugar"},{"pid":"34961932cdf24d23685dc3420f974f853c34d70a","tid":2393972,"uid":134071,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"a46dc1b226cca11c6bd2c8da05c53675a771570a","tid":2393972,"uid":179729,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T01:16:54.000Z","msg":"Guyana依個地方有特別？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T01:19:29.000Z","msg":"（三立篇文有講）<br />\n<br />\n。。。<br />\n<br />\n第二個重大意義，是蓋國經濟發展具潛力，台蓋經貿合作遠景可期。涉外人士提到，蓋亞那人口數約為78萬人，2019年之國家生產毛額（GDP）約為68億美金，國民平均所得為6,609美元。蓋國2019年經濟成長率為5.35%，位居全球第三，表現亮眼；據IMF統計，蓋國2020年的預估經濟成長率更可達26.2%。並且蓋國擁有豐富的原油、黃金、鋁土、鑽石、各式稀有金屬礦藏及林木資源。對於充滿經濟前景的國家，我國樂願趁著這個機會，分享我們發展的經驗，共同協助蓋國發展，並且為台商發掘商機。<br />\n<br />\n涉外人士指出，第三個重大意義，是這個地理位置非常重要，設代表處有助對南美洲東北角之經營。蓋亞那位處南美洲東北部要衝，係聯繫南美洲及加勒比海的窗口，故「加勒比海共同體」（CARICOM）將其秘書處設於蓋國首都喬治城，其重要性可見一斑。加上加勒比海地區是我國外交重鎮，我國在加海地區有貝里斯、海地及三聖共5個邦交國，蓋國在地緣上亦屬加勒比海國家，為「加勒比海共同體」（CARICOM）及「加勒比海國家聯盟」（ACS）的正式會員，於蓋國設處可增進我國在加海地區的連結。且南美洲東北部幅員廣大，除蓋亞那外，尚有有委內瑞拉、法屬圭亞那及蘇利南，我國自2009年9月15日裁撤駐委內瑞拉代表處迄今，在南美東北部需要積極經營，本案有助未來拓展相關業務並提昇我國的能見度，並推動我與該區域的實質關係。<br />\n<br />\n涉外人士也說，第四個重大意義，是蓋國持續深化民主，與美國關係友好，是理念相近國家。。。。。"},{"pid":"a43e6c3bbda73476952478e7c264ca3bf2c22cd9","tid":2393972,"uid":151525,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a46dc1b226cca11c6bd2c8da05c53675a771570a","tid":2393972,"uid":179729,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":