ps://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=422995\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D422995&d=f02Xtm2mX5FaAGCExHUdjctxnk%2BhbBpP3j1S%2FgfPRD4%3D&h=c2169d27\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D422995&h=5f7d2593\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=422995</a><br />\n圭亞那終止台灣於當地設立辦公室協議"}]}